org.jppf.server.protocol

Class AbstractCommonSLA

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jppf.server.protocol.AbstractCommonSLA
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, JobCommonSLA
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JPPFJobClientSLA, JPPFJobSLA

    public abstract class AbstractCommonSLA
extends Object
implements JobCommonSLA
    This class represents the Service Level Agreement Between a JPPF job and a server. It determines the state, conditions and order in which a job will be executed.
    See Also:
